12.short_description: Sibo Energy SA is a Costa Rican company specializing in photovoltaic solar energy,

18.description:
Sibo Energy is focused on the development of technology solutions to generate electricity with solar power. It offers a photovoltaic solar panel system for residential, commercial, and institutional properties. The company operates facilities such as the National Power and Light, the Costa Rican Electricity Institute, the Cooperative Rural Electrification of Guanacaste, the Cooperative Rural Electrification of San Carlos, and the Public Service Company of Heredia.

Sibo Energy provides solutions that enable its customers to monitor their solar panels through their PCs, mobile phones, and tablets online.

Sibo Energy was founded by Edgar Soley in 2012. It is based in San Jose, California.
